{"tid":1686961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳乾旱嚴重致大豆產量銳減 大豆價格料將持續上漲","createTime":"2019-11-01T13:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T17:08:38.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bf36c5fa3bf0b8675267452265fb7520c224163","tid":1686961,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"澳乾旱嚴重致大豆產量銳減 大豆價格料將持續上漲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20191029/33119058.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20191029%2F33119058.html&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvLTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=2b01d201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20191029/33119058.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中新網10月29日電 據澳大利亞《星島日報》報導，因乾旱少雨，澳大利亞的大豆產量下降了80%，預計大豆價格上漲將持續到2020年。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，一般來說，每噸澳大利亞大豆的價格為500澳元，但在2018年，由於缺乏雨水，澳大利亞大豆的價格升至約850澳元，預計到2020年將升至每噸1000澳元。<br />\n<br />\n一位澳農業協會的官員表示，2018年的大豆收成是澳北海岸有史以來最差的。他還表示，因為乾旱太嚴重了，2018年當地最大的大豆生產商甚至根本沒有種植。<br />\n<br />\n一位大豆種植者表示，因乾旱，他們在過去兩年裡損失了200萬澳元。澳大利亞最大的豆奶供貨商之一&mdash;&mdash;維他奶集團也表示，他們不得不從海外採購豆奶。<br />\n<br />\n澳大利亞餐飲行業協會行政總裁表示，由於嚴重乾旱，該行業面臨著嚴重的成本壓力，消費者將不得不面對飲食方面的加價。"},{"pid":"2d9ce2fb3039c498d52bc540ce3dab0ee4a460cd","tid":1686961,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E6Wf9PV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE6Wf9PV.png&h=cfdaea95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"feebd17407d34ed6e97a48ffb78be25353481b5e","tid":1686961,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3d2920280d930f75746f5fe5d53faa601ba66e","tid":1686961,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:30:59.000Z","msg":"climate change <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班澳洲佬仲要開新煤礦 抵你地連大豆都種唔到"},{"pid":"5f68e559d581b50dc8802029a38c8e5ddae43088","tid":1686961,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f783946dccf4c38d168c0b8fd4149e5b4a23730b","tid":1686961,"uid":322955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"澳豆的產量不高<br />\n而且是非基改<br />\n賣給人吃的為主<br />\n<br />\n美豆加豆是基改豆<br />\n賣給豬吃的為主"}]}